        <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="weui-footer__link">关注无极玄服务</a>
        <a href="contactUs" class="weui-footer__link">联系我们</a>
    </p>
    <p class="weui-footer__text">Copyright © 2017 芜湖雁脉传媒文化有限公司版权所有</p>
</div>

